data.description: Location is convenient to most everything in Cruces.  We have huge trees which provide shade from the heat, also productive fruit trees including peach, pear, apple and apricot.  On this pie shaped, safe piece of property, there are many outdoor private sitting areas to enjoy the birds chirping here in the middle of town.  Only three families have lived here in the 50 years it has been here.  Each improvements to a choice piece of paradise. We have installed mini blinds, tiled high use areas, carpet in the back half of the home, 2-person jacuzzi tub in the front bathroom, 2 skylights and 1 sky tube.  Each room has been painted fresh.  There are four out-buildings; game room (with pool table), mother-in-law quarters, 2"x4"playhouse w/ refrigerated air, shop and storage, which don't add to sq footage, but greatly increase livability, comfort and pleasure.
data.whatILove: We have loved raising our family and grandchild here in complete safety.  The abundance of fruit from June through November has been wonderful.  The large, mature  trees have provided shade during the heat of the summer, for yards, cars, and house, thus reducing energy bills.
